  m_Name: D4FMD
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueHidesSubmit: 1
  lines:
  - You got the site info?
  - "You: Oh, yes. I wrote down what I found on it. I\u2019ll send over a scan."
  - "\u2026"
  - "Seems all those outsiders are as gullible as the cattle in here\u2026. maybe
    we could have got some actual fucking help by now if they had an ounce of critical
    thinking."
  - But no surprises in the rest of it, just more inconsistencies with the bullshit
    they fed us as always.
  - "Either way\u2026 good work, I\u2019ve got some more info to share. "
  - "Lines up perfectly will at that shit I said yesterday, doesn\u2019t it? Probably
    some links to the spy investigation aswell with the \u201Coutsider information\u201D."
  - "Speaking of, he wants a word with you today. You\u2019ll see him at some point,
    name will be like Ivan or something? Pretty tall guy, and he\u2019ll give you
    the friendly, talkative, bullshit you get from everyone around here."
  - "Codeword FACTION and he\u2019ll drop the act give you the real him."
  - 'You: Alright, thanks.'
  - "\u2026."
  - 'You: Everything alright?'
  - "We uuh\u2026 we were in the same school class, right? You were that little friendless
    kid that sat near the back."
  - 'You: Huh? Oh, yeah. You were right at the back right? But, you would always
    push others away.'
  - "Well maybe if the teachers did the job they\u2019re PAID to do and actually
    helped me I wouldn\u2019t have had to "
  - "You: Why didn\u2019t you talk to them about it?"
  - "Why didn\u2019t THEY talk to ME about it? They were perfectly fine helping everyone
    else, weren\u2019t they?"
  - "Whatever, it doesn\u2019t matter, just look out for the spy."
  bridgeAfterDialogue: 0
